dct_title_s: Tabula exactissima regnorum Sueciae et Norvegiae
dct_description_sm: A. Nicolao Iohannide Piscatore ; Abraham Goos sculpsit.
Bar scale on map given in: "Scala miliarium".
North oriented toward upper right of sheet.
Dedication to "Gustavo Adolpho D. G." in title cartouche.
Decorative cartouche bordered by coat of arms, decorative border, dedication in upper right, descriptive text, compass rose, vegetation, icons of buildings and animals.
Dutch gothic text: De Noort Zee; De Oost Zee.
